T14TD4325E:96b-1: a'a yu ga ni ta pha la bra ka sha n'a ma /
T14TD4325E:96b-3: tshe rtsis kyi 'bras bu gsal bar byed ba zhes bya ba /
T14TD4325E:96b-5: gnas skabs bzhin shes skyes bu yis //
T14TD4325E:96b-6: dang po'i gnas skabs gsal 'dod na //
T14TD4325E:97a-1: nyi drug sogs lo yis bsgyur //
T14TD4325E:97a-2: de la mkha' nyis bgos thob lo //
T14TD4325E:97a-3: dag na kun bsdoms mkha' nyid grub //
T14TD4325E:97a-4: so so'i me rnams mkha' dus mes //
T14TD4325E:97a-5: bsgyur te mkha' nyis rnyed brtan pa'o //
T14TD4325E:97a-6: rang rang brtan pa drug sogs bsgyur //
T14TD4325E:97a-7: mkha' dus me yis thob pa lo //
T14TD4325E:97a-8: lhag ma mkha' mes thob zla ba //
T14TD4325E:97a-9: de yi lhag ma zhag tu 'gyur //
T14TD4325E:97a-10: dag na rang lo'i 'gro ldog nges //
T14TD4325E:97a-11: dang po'i cha shas nges rgyas shes //
T14TD4325E:97a-12: brgya sogs gsum la'ang drug la sogs //
T14TD4325E:97a-13: gza' dgu so so'i lo yis bsgre //
T14TD4325E:97a-14: mkha' dang nyi mas thob pa lo //
T14TD4325E:97a-15: lhag la nam mkha' me yis /
T14TD4325E:97a-17: thob pa zla ba lhag ma zhag / de nas so so'i lo rnams kun //
T14TD4325E:97a-18: mkha' dus me yis bsgyur bar bya //
T14TD4325E:97a-19: zla ba mkha' mes bsgres pa sbyin //
T14TD4325E:97a-20: mkha' ros rnyed pa brtan pa zhag / lhag ma drug cus thob chu chod //
T14TD4325E:97a-21: de nas rang rang brtan pa rnams //
T14TD4325E:97a-22: drug la sogs pa'i rang los bsgre //
T14TD4325E:97a-23: mkha' dus mes ba gos thob pa lo //
T14TD4325E:97a-24: gal te rnyed par ma gyur na //
T14TD4325E:97a-25: mkha' mes bgos la zla ba bya //
T14TD4325E:97a-26: de yi lhag ma zhag tu 'gyur //
T14TD4325E:97a-27: dag na lnga sogs rang gi lo //
T14TD4325E:97a-28: dgu tshan re la 'gro ldog nges //
T14TD4325E:97a-29: cha shas phyi ma rgyas pa'o //
T14TD4325E:97a-30: cha shas re re drug cha re //
T14TD4325E:97a-31: phri bas brtan pa'ang drug cha 'bri //
T14TD4325E:97a-32: de ni rtsis kyi gzhi ma yin //
T14TD4325E:97a-33: bsgyur dang 'god byed mtshungs par ldan //
T14TD4325E:97a-34: de ltar zla klu rnams gzhi shes //
T14TD4325E:97a-35: gzhan yang tshe yi snod 'brid dang //
T14TD4325E:97a-36: bslu zhing bsring ba'i chog rnams //
T14TD4325E:97a-37: khong du chud nas ston par gyis //
T14TD4325E:97a-39: ji snyed mkhyen pas bsgyur ba'o //
T14TD4325E:97a-40: tshe 'bras kyi rtsis gsal bar byed pa ma na pu ru shas mdzad pa /
T14TD4325E:97a-41: aithi na ka ra ka ta'i bram ze lag ma ti dang /
